Package com.tcs.entity

Class Underwriter

java.lang.Object
com.tcs.entity.Underwriter
@Entity public class Underwriter extends Object
Entity representing an Underwriter in the insurance system. Each Underwriter has a corresponding login and can manage multiple vehicles.
